le S4</a>. Dotted lines indicate cross-verified for which evidence of a signal is apparent in regions from other studies, but did not pass our criteria for inclusion (See <a href="#s3">Materials and Methods</a> and <a href="#pone-0001712-g007">Figures 7</a> and <a href="#pone-0001712-g008">8</a>).</p>
